            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p><a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/facility-rentals?facility_rentals_facets%5B0%5D=facility%3ADempsey%20Community%20Centre">Enquire about availability and/or reserve a space with this facility</a>.</p>
<p>The City of Ottawa has hundreds of indoor and outdoor spaces suitable for special events, meetings, sports, and gatherings of all kinds. <a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities-and-rentals/rental-information">Find out more</a>.</p>
